Docker #4: Using Docker Hub

https://hub.docker.com/

You can search docker hub and use the images from your terminal.
Tims-Macbook-Pro-2:KituraDocker timbeals$ docker search ibmcom

To get the image that you want use the pull command
Tims-Macbook-Pro-2:KituraDocker timbeals$ docker pull (NAME)

check that you have the image
Tims-Macbook-Pro-2:KituraDocker timbeals$ docker images

spin up the container
Tims-Macbook-Pro-2:KituraDocker timbeals$ docker run -itv $(pwd):/root -w /root --name swift-ubuntu -p 8090:8090 ibmcom/swift-ubuntu /bin/bash


